&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.rogerlinndesign.com/&#34;&gt;Roger Linn Design&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.rogerlinndesign.com/linnstrument&#34;&gt;LinnStrument&lt;/a&gt; - expressive MIDI controller for musical performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://roli.com/&#34;&gt;Roli&lt;/a&gt;
