&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://roli.com/products/blocks/seaboard-block-m&#34;&gt;Seaboard BLOCK M&lt;/a&gt; - compact and powerful, play any sound imaginable and express yourself effortlessly — wherever creativity finds you — on this evolution of the multi-award-winning original&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://roli.com/products/seaboard/rise2&#34;&gt;Seaboard RISE 2&lt;/a&gt; - a keyboard designed for limitless exploration of sound&lt;/li&gt;
